***O(N+E)*** :
The adjacency list representation of the graph takes O(E) space, where E is the number of edges. Additionally, the "visited" vector, "distance_node1" and "distance_node2" vectors all take O(N) space, where N is the number of nodes. So, the overall space complexity is O(N+E).

