if node ie specified by index is rechable by both nodes i.e it have dist >=0 in both vector then we will take maximum of that and keep track of it
Like 
here we have node 0 with distance 5,6 so we will take dist (6,0) ans we have to take maximum among these two and minimum among this and other distances
Like wise other pairs will be
(1,1) , (3,2), (5, 3), (4, 7), (2,8), (6, 7) we cant reach 4,5,6 
so from these distances we need minimum one which is 1 and it is corresponding to node ('1') so we return node 1;

