# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Get the distance from node1 and node2 to all other nodes, visit  every node and get the minimum distance so far

# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(n)$$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: $$O(n)$$
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
